<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>China News | Today's Breaking Stories | Reuters</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/reuters/world/china" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><description>Reuters.com is your online source for the latest China news stories and current events, ensuring our readers up to date with any breaking news developments - Powered by RSSHub</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>contact@rsshub.app (RSSHub)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://www.reuters.com/pf/resources/images/reuters/logo-vertical-default-512x512.png?d=116</url><title>China News | Today's Breaking Stories | Reuters</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 02:49:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>180</ttl><item><title>Rho Motion 称，7 月份全球电动汽车销量增长 21%，中国创下 2024 年最大增幅</title><description>市场研究公司 Rho Motion 周一表示，尽管欧洲需求下降，但得益于中国今年最强劲的增长，7 月份全电动和插电式混合动力汽车的全球销量同比增长 21%。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-21-july-china-records-biggest-jump-2024-rho-motion-says-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">IJWPJP2K6JPRLCPEZTTLVF3TIU</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 23:06:48 GMT</pubDate><author>Alessandro Parodi</author><category>Business</category><category>Autos &amp; Transportation</category></item><item><title>早间买盘：新发现的市场平静等待动荡的考验</title><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">DH36RJDH6VOVLFTZMRCK254XFA</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 21:49:56 GMT</pubDate><author>Lewis Krauskopf</author><category>Markets</category><category>Asian Markets</category></item><item><title>欧佩克下调石油需求增长预期，凸显10月加息的困境</title><description>OPEC 周一下调了 2024 年全球石油需求增长预测，理由是对中国的预期疲软，这一下调凸显了更广泛的 OPEC+ 集团在 10 月份起增产方面面临的困境。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/opec-cuts-2024-oil-demand-growth-forecast-citing-china-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">AGAOQRAC7FPWPDYJIM6YUTDZPE</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 10:46:59 GMT</pubDate><author>Alex Lawler</author><category>Business</category><category>Energy</category></item><item><title>越南新任党总书记将于下周访华</title><description>三名知情官员告诉路透社，越南最高领导人苏林将于下周访问中国，这是他自八月初被任命为执政的共产党总书记以来的首次出访。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-newly-appointed-party-chief-set-visit-china-next-week-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">HMM6YXOUPRJTBM2IYX2CQPM6MQ</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>World</category><category>Asia Pacific</category></item><item><title>韩国和美国将针对朝鲜导弹和网络威胁举行年度演习</title><description>官员周一表示，韩国和美国将于下周开始年度夏季军事演习，以提高应对朝鲜武器和网络威胁的能力。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-over-norths-missile-cyber-threats-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">IIFU77V44FIZJFLR2EKWBBIEWY</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 06:47:09 GMT</pubDate><author>Hyonhee Shin</author><category>World</category></item><item><title>随着低空经济的加速，中国试验货运无人机和空中出租车</title><description>周末，工程师们派出了中国迄今为止最大的货运无人机进行试运行，同时一架直升机出租车在即将开通的通往上海的 100 公里（62 英里）航线上飞上了天空，为中国不断扩大的低空运输奠定了新的里程碑——高原经济。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-test-flies-biggest-cargo-drone-low-altitude-economy-takes-off-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">KHC7QCCFQNOEFHG3JCAJFDJVYM</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:53:31 GMT</pubDate><author>Ryan Woo</author><category>World</category><category>China</category></item><item><title>黄岩岛空难事件后菲律宾敦促中国缓和紧张局势</title><description>菲律宾周一敦促北京留意缓解南海紧张局势的呼吁，此前菲律宾空军在两国同意更好地管理海上争端后采取了“非常危险”的行动。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-file-protest-with-china-over-air-force-incident-over-south-china-sea-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">CB44KVMPJ5IQFLP2JSMUITW4AU</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:40:19 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>World</category><category>Asia Pacific</category></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">6WX4JNPBENK6FLJYPQEO74WLAE</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:21:43 GMT</pubDate><author>Michael Church</author><category>Sports</category><category>Soccer</category></item><item><title>香港法院驳回媒体大亨黎智英推翻定罪的请求</title><description>香港最高法院周一一致驳回了推翻媒体大亨黎智英和其他六名民主运动人士2019年未经授权集会定罪的请求。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-by-media-tycoon-jimmy-lai-overturn-conviction-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">2ODO6I3LYBPU3GLCHKS2FXQD5A</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:21:16 GMT</pubDate><author>Jessie Pang</author><category>World</category><category>China</category></item><item><title>香港法院推迟中国佳兆业集团清算听证会</title><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求佳兆业集团清算的请愿书的听证会推迟至 9 月 9 日，这使得这家陷入困境的中国开发商有更多时间与一些债券持有人就其债务重组计划达成协议。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-kaisa-group-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-by-hong-kong-court-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">QPLK2J2Y5FIMDGI4EG6LGOHLUU</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 01:49:26 GMT</pubDate><author>Clare Jim, Yu Xie</author><category>Sustainability</category><category>Boards, Policy &amp; Regulation</category></item><item><title>央行与多头对峙，中国国债市场动荡</title><description>中国央行一再警告称，随着投资者追逐政府债券、逃离动荡的股票和不断下滑的房地产市场，可能存在破坏稳定的泡沫风险。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-bond-market-rattled-central-bank-squares-off-with-bond-bulls-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">GF4RXOA3LFIBVLVZVAX7ADDDOM</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:04:55 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Sustainability</category><category>Boards, Policy &amp; Regulation</category></item><item><title>外交部长表示，中国支持伊朗捍卫安全</title><description>据中国外交部的一份声明称，中国外交部长王毅周日在电话中告诉伊朗代理外长，中国支持伊朗捍卫其“主权、安全和民族尊严”。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-iran-defending-security-says-foreign-minister-2024-08-11/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">V6777RGMHVNAPPSDKQT43DCLIA</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 11:21:36 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>World</category></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国空军的行动“非法”、“鲁莽”</title><description>中国表示，菲律宾扰乱了其训练，并指责马尼拉“非法侵入”其领空。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-actions-china-air-force-illegal-reckless-2024-08-11/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">MKDPESN4KRM4LLJT63TZKZZBSA</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 06:39:41 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>World</category><category>Asia Pacific</category></item><item><title>菲律宾与中国就南海问题进行贸易指责</title><description>这是自2022年小费迪南德·马科斯总统就职以来菲律宾首次抱怨中国飞机的危险行为。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-condemns-china-air-force-dangerous-acts-south-china-sea-2024-08-10/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">VQILWDOQAVI7JCVBGTH4TBMOWE</guid><pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 09:26:58 GMT</pubDate><author>Neil Morales</author><category>World</category><category>Asia Pacific</category></item><item><title>中国火箭解体使1000多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险</title><description>分析人士周五表示，中国的一枚火箭级本周在太空中解体，产生了 700 多块碎片，使地球轨道交通繁忙区域的 1000 多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险碰撞的风险。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">VSYNV3BSUVPB7P4NEKMSTRQDXQ</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:03:13 GMT</pubDate><author>Joey Roulette</author><category>Space</category></item><item><title>央行称将增加国债交易</title><description>中国人民银行还将寻求降低企业融资和家庭信贷成本。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-says-it-will-increase-treasury-bond-trading-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">UZWROSOA2ZNIZJFQIZDC3N6UEE</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 18:47:11 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Markets</category><category>Rates &amp; Bonds</category></item><item><title>欧盟高管表示调查仍在继续，相信其中国电动汽车措施符合世贸组织</title><description>欧盟执行机构周五表示，欧盟委员会相信其对中国电动汽车国家补贴的调查和针对中国电动汽车补贴的措施符合世界贸易组织的规则，并将继续进行调查。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-executive-confident-its-chinese-ev-measures-comply-with-wto-says-probe-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">3GPSO6ZKJRIDXDGB4P5YDOVWRQ</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 15:37:08 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Business</category><category>Autos &amp; Transportation</category></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人要求投资者加入重组程序</title><description>中国恒大在周五提交的文件中表示，其清算人已邀请有兴趣重组这家负债累累的房地产开发商或其任何部分的投资者。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">CQM25NG5CJOHNG5RL63NVSVOZA</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:48:54 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Business</category><category>Finance</category></item><item><title>随着国内航空公司向海外扩张，外国航空公司对中国失去了兴趣</title><description>由于俄罗斯广阔空域飞往欧洲和北美的北方航线较短，中国航空公司享有成本优势。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">XG2PVHKM2BMJPEAM6GAMOWEEJU</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:56:30 GMT</pubDate><author>Lisa Barrington</author><category>Business</category><category>Aerospace &amp; Defense</category></item><item><title>天气因素导致中国消费价格上涨；国内需求依然疲软</title><description>中国脆弱的消费领域一直是北京关注的主要焦点，因为疲软的内需拖累了世界第二大经济体，同时制造业活动萎缩。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">NLNVKPYOIRPNJJEBHOMXE4OOSY</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:37:58 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Markets</category><category>Asian Markets</category></item></channel></rss>